pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: page-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 40, 900, 40]
    content:
      style: "$pageTitle"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Schema de Base de Donnees — 5 Tables Cles</strong></p>
  - elementId: title-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 85, 100, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border: {style: solid, width: 3, color: "$accent"}
  - elementId: schema-table
    elementType: table
    bounds: [60, 110, 1160, 520]
    columnWidths: [0.18, 0.22, 0.60]
    rowHeights: [0.1, 0.18, 0.18, 0.18, 0.18, 0.18]
    style: "$default"
    rows:
      - - content:
            text: |
              <p><strong>Table</strong></p>
        - content:
            text: |
              <p><strong>Cles</strong></p>
        - content:
            text: |
              <p><strong>Description</strong></p>
      - - content:
            text: |
              <p><strong>users</strong></p>
        - content:
            text: |
              <p>id, unionId, role</p>
        - content:
            text: |
              <p>Utilisateurs authentifies via Kimi OAuth. Role : commercial | directeur | admin. Stocke nom, email, avatar.</p>
      - - content:
            text: |
              <p><strong>companies</strong></p>
        - content:
            text: |
              <p>id, name, color</p>
        - content:
            text: |
              <p>Entreprises clientes. Chaque entreprise a un nom, des notes, une couleur associee et un createur (FK vers users).</p>
      - - content:
            text: |
              <p><strong>projects</strong></p>
        - content:
            text: |
              <p>id, code, ownerId</p>
        - content:
            text: |
              <p>Projets avec code AIM-XXXX. Chaque projet appartient a une entreprise et a un proprietaire (FK vers users). Status : active | won | lost | archived.</p>
      - - content:
            text: |
              <p><strong>projectFiles</strong></p>
        - content:
            text: |
              <p>id, projectId, stepId</p>
        - content:
            text: |
              <p>Fichiers associes a un projet et a une etape du processus (ex: "chiffrage", "reception"). Stocke nom, type, taille, date.</p>
      - - content:
            text: |
              <p><strong>projectMembers</strong></p>
        - content:
            text: |
              <p>projectId, userId, permission</p>
        - content:
            text: |
              <p><strong>Table cle pour le RBAC.</strong> Lien utilisateur-projet avec permission : owner (plein controle) | editor (modification) | viewer (lecture) | pending (en attente).</p>
  - elementId: note
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 635, 1160, 22]
    content:
      fontSize: 13
      color: "$secondary"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [left, middle]
      text: |
        <p>Toutes les tables utilisent des cles etrangeres (FK) avec contraintes ON DELETE. Relations : users 1-N projects (owner), users 1-N projectMembers, projects N-N users via projectMembers.</p>
  - elementId: bottom-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 660, 1160, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border: {style: solid, width: 1, color: "$light"}
  - elementId: page-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1150, 670, 70, 20]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "$secondary"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "10"